                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5126" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0068</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8505 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">疫情来袭寒冬至  工会变革迎春风 ——吉利控股集团“中国特色企业工会”新探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Case Study of Geely’s Labor Union Organization Reform During the Novel Coronavirus Epidemic</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谢嗣胜，郑天宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京航空航天大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉利控股集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉利控股集团工会；新冠疫情；中国特色企业工会；工会组织变革；工会职能创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Geely’s Labor Union; Novel Coronavirus Epidemic; Enterprise Labor Union with Chinese Characteristics; Organization Reform; Functional Innovation of Labor Union</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当前受疫情影响，不少企业的生存发展面临挑战，职工权益保障也遇到一些困难问题，企业工会在统筹推进疫情防控与复工复产、协调劳动关系、动员广大职工特别是新生代员工与企业同舟共济、共渡难关等方面大有可为。本案例以吉利控股集团工会副主席封飞行为案例线索，按照企业疫情防控与复工复产工作的时间进程，通过主人翁的系列工作活动，揭示传统工会普遍存在的一些不足，探索构建吉利控股集团特色民企工会新模式，建立和谐稳定的社会主义新型劳动关系，促进企业发展，确保职工共享企业发展成果。案例力图使学员了解中国特色社会主义工会本质特征，掌握新时代的企业工会理论与创新。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Affected by the Novel Coronavirus Epidemic, many enterprises faced challenges in their survival and development. There are also some difficulties in protecting the rights and interests of employees. Labor unions are not only involved in the prevention and control of epidemic in enterprises and local areas. Labor unions can also play a huge role in helping enterprises to resume work, coordinating labor relations. Labor unions also have the ability to motivate employees, especially the new generation of employees, to work together with enterprises to overcome difficulties and promote social harmony and stability. In this case, Feng Feixing, vice chairman of the Geely’s Labor Union, is the main character. According to the time clues, we describe a series of work carried out by Geely’s Labor Union during the Novel Coronavirus Epidemic, which reveals some deficiencies that traditional Labor unions generally have. The Geely’s Labor Union also explored the construction of a labor union model with Geely’s characteristics, forming new model of harmonious labor relations, collaborate on enterprise development and sharing the fruits of reform and development. It is hoped that through the study of the case, students will be able to understand the nature and functions of labor union with Chinese characteristics and master the theory of labor union organization reform.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《劳动关系管理》、《组织行为学》、《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工会建设、组织变革、新时代员工管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-01</td>
                            </tr>
